                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipit of Text I; directives to the
                           ministers and their abbreviations; titles of the books to be read;
                           elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; quire
                           marks. 
 On the incipit page of Text I (fol. 3r), few lines are
                           rubricated (alternating with two black lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
